## 2. Input field

### 2.1 Default input

- **Container bg:** `c.generalBackgroundBgL1`
- **Border:** `c.generalStrokeL2` (default), `c.actionBackgroundPrimary` (focused), `c.negativeBackgroundPrimary` (error)
- **Radius:** `s.cornerRadiusInputInput` (8)
- **Label (above field):** `f.bodyR` (12/16), color `c.generalForegroundSecondary`
- **Input value text:** `f.uiTextR` (14/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Placeholder / hint:** `f.uiTextR` (14/20), color `c.generalForegroundTertiary`
- **Error text (below):** `f.bodyR` (12/16), color `c.negativeBackgroundPrimary`
- **Content padding:** horizontal `s.sizeInputInputH` (16), vertical `s.sizeInputInputV` (6)

```dart
Column(
  crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
  children: [
    Text('Label', style: f.bodyR.copyWith(color: c.generalForegroundSecondary)),
    SizedBox(height: s.sizeGeneralXXS),
    TextField(
      style: f.uiTextR.copyWith(color: c.generalForegroundPrimary),
      decoration: InputDecoration(
        hintText: 'Placeholder',
        hintStyle: f.uiTextR.copyWith(color: c.generalForegroundTertiary),
        contentPadding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(
          horizontal: s.sizeInputInputH,
          vertical: s.sizeInputInputV,
        ),
        filled: true,
        fillColor: c.generalBackgroundBgL1,
        border: OutlineInputBorder(
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusInputInput),
          borderSide: BorderSide(color: c.generalStrokeL2),
        ),
        enabledBorder: OutlineInputBorder(
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusInputInput),
          borderSide: BorderSide(color: c.generalStrokeL2),
        ),
        focusedBorder: OutlineInputBorder(
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusInputInput),
          borderSide: BorderSide(color: c.actionBackgroundPrimary),
        ),
        errorBorder: OutlineInputBorder(
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusInputInput),
          borderSide: BorderSide(color: c.negativeBackgroundPrimary),
        ),
      ),
    ),
  ],
)
```

### 2.2 Hero input (large numeric)

- **Text style:** `f.lHeadlineSB` (20/24) or `f.xlHeadlineSB` (24/28)
- **No border;** underline or borderless style

