## 4. Header / AppBar

### 4.1 Standard header (L2 — white background)

- **Background:** `c.generalBackgroundBgL1`
- **Title:** `f.headlineSB` (16/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Back icon:** size 24, color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Action icons:** size 24, color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Bottom border:** `c.generalStrokeL1`

### 4.2 Accent header (colored background)

- **Background:** `c.actionBackgroundPrimary`
- **Title:** `f.headlineSB` (16/20), color `c.actionForegroundPrimary`
- **Icons:** color `c.actionForegroundPrimary`

### 4.3 Tab bar below header

- **Active tab:** `f.headlineSB` (16/20), color `c.actionBackgroundPrimary` (on white bg) or `c.actionForegroundPrimary` (on accent bg), with 2px underline
- **Inactive tab:** `f.headlineR` (16/20), color `c.generalForegroundTertiary` (on white bg) or `c.actionForegroundPrimary` at 60% opacity (on accent bg)

