## 7. Toast / Snackbar

- **Radius:** `s.cornerRadiusGeneralXS` (8)
- **Text style:** `f.uiTextM` (14/20, weight 500)
- **Text color:** white (`c.actionForegroundPrimary`)
- **Leading indicator:** 8px circle, white
- **Padding:** horizontal `s.sizeGeneralM` (16), vertical `s.sizeGeneralS` (12)

**Variants:**

| Variant | Background |
|---|---|
| Success | `c.positiveBackgroundPrimary` |
| Error | `c.negativeBackgroundPrimary` |
| Warning | `c.alertBackgroundPrimary` |
| Neutral | `c.generalBackgroundBgL3` (text: `c.generalForegroundPrimary`) |

```dart
Container(
  width: double.infinity,
  padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(
    horizontal: s.sizeGeneralM,
    vertical: s.sizeGeneralS,
  ),
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: c.positiveBackgroundPrimary,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusGeneralXS),
  ),
  child: Row(
    children: [
      Container(
        width: 8,
        height: 8,
        decoration: const BoxDecoration(
          color: Colors.white,
          shape: BoxShape.circle,
        ),
      ),
      SizedBox(width: s.sizeGeneralS),
      Expanded(
        child: Text(
          'Toast message goes here',
          style: f.uiTextM.copyWith(color: c.actionForegroundPrimary),
        ),
      ),
    ],
  ),
)
```

