## 9. Cards

- **Background:** `c.generalBackgroundBgL1`
- **Radius:** `s.cornerRadiusCardCard` (16) for standard, `s.cornerRadiusCardSCard` (8) for compact
- **Border:** `c.generalStrokeL2`
- **Padding:** `s.sizeGeneralM` (16) all sides
- **Title:** `f.uiTextSB` (14/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Subtitle / secondary:** `f.bodyR` (12/16), color `c.generalForegroundSecondary`
- **Divider inside card:** `c.generalStrokeL1`

```dart
Container(
  padding: EdgeInsets.all(s.sizeGeneralM),
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: c.generalBackgroundBgL1,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusCardCard),
    border: Border.all(color: c.generalStrokeL2),
  ),
  child: Column(
    crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
    children: [
      Text('Card Title', style: f.uiTextSB.copyWith(color: c.generalForegroundPrimary)),
      SizedBox(height: s.sizeGeneralXXS),
      Text('Secondary info', style: f.bodyR.copyWith(color: c.generalForegroundSecondary)),
    ],
  ),
)
```

