## 10. List items / Selection rows

### 10.1 Simple list item

- **Leading icon:** 24px, color `c.generalForegroundSecondary`
- **Primary text:** `f.uiTextSB` (14/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Trailing icon/chevron:** 20px, color `c.generalForegroundTertiary`
- **Vertical padding:** `s.sizeGeneralS` (12)
- **Horizontal padding:** `s.sizeGeneralM` (16)

### 10.2 Two-line list item

- **Primary text:** `f.uiTextSB` (14/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Secondary text:** `f.bodyR` (12/16), color `c.generalForegroundSecondary`
- **Spacing between lines:** `s.sizeGeneralXXS` (4)

### 10.3 Selection item (with check)

- **Leading check circle:** 24px, bg `c.positiveBackgroundSecondary`, icon `c.positiveBackgroundPrimary` (when selected)
- **Text:** `f.uiTextR` (14/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Trailing indicator:** 8px circle, color `c.generalForegroundTertiary`
- **Row bg (selected):** `c.positiveBackgroundSecondary`

```dart
Container(
  padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(
    horizontal: s.sizeGeneralM,
    vertical: s.sizeGeneralS,
  ),
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: isSelected ? c.positiveBackgroundSecondary : c.generalBackgroundBgL1,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(s.cornerRadiusCardSCard),
  ),
  child: Row(
    children: [
      Icon(
        isSelected ? Icons.check_circle : Icons.circle_outlined,
        size: 24,
        color: isSelected ? c.positiveBackgroundPrimary : c.generalForegroundTertiary,
      ),
      SizedBox(width: s.sizeGeneralS),
      Expanded(
        child: Text(
          'Selection item',
          style: f.uiTextR.copyWith(color: c.generalForegroundPrimary),
        ),
      ),
      Icon(Icons.circle, size: 8, color: c.generalForegroundTertiary),
    ],
  ),
)
```

