## 12. Bottom sheet

- **Background:** `c.generalBackgroundBgL1`
- **Radius (top only):** `s.cornerRadiusBottomSheetBottomSheet` (20) for topLeft and topRight
- **Handle bar:** 36x4, color `c.generalStrokeL3`, centered, radius 2
- **Title:** `f.headlineSB` (16/20), color `c.generalForegroundPrimary`
- **Padding:** `s.sizePagePageMargin` (20) horizontal, `s.sizeGeneralM` (16) vertical

