## Quick reference — minimum font sizes

| Context | Minimum style | Size |
|---|---|---|
| Any readable body text | `uiTextR` | 14px |
| Secondary / supporting text | `bodyR` | 12px |
| Captions, field labels | `bodyR` | 12px |
| Bottom-nav labels | `labelM` | 10px |
| Tags, badges, tiny counts | `sLabelSB` | 8px |
| Never use for readable content | `xsBody`, `xsLabel` | 7–9px |
